HEADWORD: nonreversible
<hw>nonreversible</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Not reversible or capable of
having either side out; -- used mostly of clothing. Opposite of
<ant>reversible</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> one-sided.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

